parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended activation of the automatic emergency braking system can cause sudden and unexpected stops, which can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly stops or brakes without warning
often with no obstacle or vehicle in front of it; the forward collision warning light appears on the dashboard; the vehicle may jerk or lurch forward after the brakes are released.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning of the blind spot monitoring system can cause false warnings, rendering the system unreliable and potentially leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The blind spot warning lights illuminate unnecessarily
often when decelerating or braking; the system may fail to detect actual vehicles in the blind spot; the window switches and door lock button may not function when the blind spot indicators are on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause the loss of critical vehicle information, including speed, fuel level, and safety features, which can lead to accidents or other safety issues.
symptoms: The infotainment screen goes blank or becomes unresponsive; the system may not display critical information
such as speed or fuel level; the system may not allow phone calls or connections to OnStar.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning of the anti-theft alarm can cause unnecessary and frequent activations, leading to inconvenience and potential safety issues.
symptoms: The alarm sounds randomly
often with no apparent reason; the alarm may not turn off even when the doors are closed and the vehicle is locked.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning of the fuel fill system can cause fuel to spill or leak, leading to potential fire hazards or environmental damage.
symptoms: Fuel spills or leaks during refueling; the fuel tank may not fill completely
resulting in incorrect fuel level readings.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Battery Drain and Electrical System Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery drain and electrical system issues can cause the vehicle to become inoperable, leading to inconvenience and potential safety issues.
symptoms: The vehicle's battery drains overnight
requiring jump-starting; multiple error messages appear on the dashboard
including check engine lights; the vehicle may experience electrical system failures
including the infotainment system.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Erroneous Activation of Automatic Emergency Braking (AEB) System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected activation of the AEB system can cause the vehicle to brake suddenly, increasing the risk of rear-end collisions, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes or decelerates without any apparent reason
often with no warning lights or alerts; the brakes may lock up
causing the vehicle to come to a sudden stop; the driver may experience sudden jolts or jerks; the vehicle may stop suddenly
even when there are no obstacles or vehicles in front of it.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty BSWS can cause false warnings, leading to driver distraction, and potentially, accidents. In some cases, the system may fail to alert the driver of an actual vehicle in the blind spot, increasing the risk of a collision.
symptoms: The blind spot warning light illuminates randomly when no other vehicle is present
the system fails to alert the driver of an actual vehicle in the blind spot
the warning lights remain on for an extended period
even on empty roads.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sensor Issues and Auto Braking Engagement
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning sensors can cause the auto braking system to engage unnecessarily, potentially leading to accidents or injuries. The faulty system can also cause other safety features, such as the blind spot warning system, to malfunction.
symptoms: The auto braking system engages for no reason
the side mirror warning sensors turn and stay on
causing other systems to malfunction
the service door latch system error appears
and other errors related to the driver assist system.
